modName: deleteAbandoned Wine Cellar in Riverwood under the Sleeping Giant Inn
summary: Abandoned Wine Cellar with a secret in Riverwood under the Sleeping Giant Inn.
descriptionHtml:
--- I\'ll only continue if there is any interest for this mod --- 
By the way, if you got any ideas for this mod - please share in the comment field! :) Cheers!

v0.2Beta
- Changes done to the lightning in Abandoned Wine Cellar.
- Added torched (not possible to pick up) and misc to give some light in the room.
- Fixed minor bugs.

v0.1Beta
- Added the Abandoned Wine Cellar in Riverwood under the Sleeping Giant Inn.
- Minor lore-friendly plant and tree changes around entrance of the Abandoned Wine Cellar.

--- Short Description ---
Abandoned Wine Cellar with a secret in Riverwood under the Sleeping Giant Inn.
Check the wall, hint hint.

Anyways, this is a very early version and I\'m not sure if I want to continue on this, what do you think?
author: ValenwoodElf
